11 An Act relating to the Office of Management and
Enterprise Services; requiring that portions of
12 certain appropriated funds be used for certain
purposes; mandating certain transfers; requiring
13 utilization in certain manner; providing an effective
date; and declaring an emergency.
14
15
16
17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
18 SECTION 1. From the funds appropriated to the Office of
19 Management and Enterprise Services in Enrolled Senate Bill No. 1177
20 of the 2nd Session of the 60th Oklahoma Legislature, the sum of One
21 Million Nine Hundred Twenty Thousand Dollars ($1,920,000.00) shall
22 be used to provide for the Pay for Success program. The Office of
23 Management and Enterprise Services shall transfer the sum of Seven
24 Hundred Twenty Thousand Dollars ($720,000.00) to the Criminal
